{"tid":709754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"田少抽爆馬時亨：坐地鐵唔太穩陣","createTime":"2018-06-20T09:10:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T09:49:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6e8c61d15cbcf3a975d4a92cf6951310e3bcca0a","tid":709754,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T09:10:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180620/20426155\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180620%2F20426155&d=f1ak%2FKx76gFv0bJ44sDKYP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=9fd3d2df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180620%2F20426155&h=d9f7318b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180620/20426155</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月20日 <br />\n<br />\n【網民hot talk】<br />\n田少抽爆馬時亨：坐地鐵唔太穩陣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n高鐵香港段早前被踢爆列車出軌、隧道漏水及車輪異常磨損，港鐵主席馬時亨以一句「我哋（管理層）話你聽OK就得㗎喇」來回應，其後港鐵沙中綫3個車站地盤亦接連被踢爆偷工減料，卻一再拖延向政府提交報告。<br />\n<br />\n自由黨前立法會議員田北俊趁端午節，在facebook發帖「抽水」，笑言「聽講坐地鐵好似有啲唔係太穩陣，早知就扒龍舟過海啦。#端午節快樂#講下笑啫」。<br />\n<br />\n馬時亨上月回應高鐵香港段被揭連串事故時，曾豪言「我哋（管理層）話你聽OK就得㗎喇」，認為社會「一定要相信我們管理層，否則這樣下去，管理層不用睡覺了」，更批評傳媒要求更多資料「無意思」，因大家都不是技術人員。<br />\n<br />\n當時田北俊的胞弟、身兼立法會鐵路事宜小組委員會主席的前九鐵公司主席田北辰，則暗批馬時亨，形容對方作風跟自己在任時不同，「我做九鐵主席時好詳盡解釋，就為了釋除公眾疑慮」，亦會不厭其煩，解答記者問題，「我會製造一個好氣氛同形象」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民點睇<br />\n<br />\nAlbert So：有內幕，田二少告知。<br />\n<br />\nClement Jim：田少，馬生話畀你聽ok就得㗎啦。<br />\n<br />\nBearbear Ying：點解你識用八達通㗎？<br />\n<br />\nMichael Yeung：扒龍舟都唔得，個海畀你抽到冇曬水。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n八方析時務：葉劉爭條鐵表忠　超區行情看漲 (李八方)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n中女中佬開餅廠　8個老死追創業夢"},{"pid":"f80ccff37de4e31d7c88ff5b5d6d2e1acd4294f9","tid":709754,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T09:26:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"872f2b61f8a6cc4db42922fcae12a9cff63acf4e","tid":709754,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T09:27:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0h2xr7tZX_bVdPTkAT_n4SAHUYbjh8In5UK3g8SBAgM2MxfShSIS8kOWxPZGNidioJJikkOGNMdmZren1VcSwk/w644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0h2xr7tZX_bVdPTkAT_n4SAHUYbjh8In5UK3g8SBAgM2MxfShSIS8kOWxPZGNidioJJikkOGNMdmZren1VcSwk%2Fw644&h=cb4a1ca6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n班友已經笑唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f52646c1595ae0a8e263727bd788ee06053d90","tid":709754,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T09:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64664718478fc2a15c238224168fa71558356f83","tid":709754,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T09:29:41.000Z","msg":"馬屎坑無料充大頭<br />\n自以為係奶共精英, 根本騎唔住班工程佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c470ece59eec1e1b520315d95c910cb2d46b36","tid":709754,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T09:31:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當年局長, 財金官員, <br />\n無人敢搵佢做司長<br />\n反而比條爛鬼會計師樓既會計仔爬頭上位做財政司司長 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家反而比運房局局長監管<br />\n個機構比政府監管<br />\n連運輸署署長亦騎住佢, 要聽運輸署同路政署講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點都好最葡萄既甜不神都係坐唔返呢個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"6a761580368ed20a191af9df2080903d1270f711","tid":709754,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64664718478fc2a15c238224168fa71558356f83","tid":709754,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T09:29:41.000Z","msg":"馬屎坑無料充大頭<br />\n自以為係奶共精英, 根本騎唔住班工程佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T09:49:25.000Z","msg":"讀到咩大學都好<br />\n冇料既人就係冇料"}]}